Node.Notes: In Ezekiel 9 and 10, several cases of passive participle of Strong no. 3847 wrongly linked with 3830 and parsed as adjective. (HALOT says there are 14 cases of this participial form that looks identical to the noun 3830, half of which are in Ezekiel.)
Morph should probably be changed to verb qal passive participle ms absolute.
